      <title>记录博客的搭建</title>
      <link href="/2021/11/12/%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/"/>
      <url>/2021/11/12/%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>[TOC]</p><h1 id="🎃写在前面…"><a href="#🎃写在前面…" class="headerlink" title="🎃写在前面…"></a>🎃写在前面…</h1><p>🚌搭好自己的博客后仿佛有了自己的小窝，好快乐~ 先这里记录一下痛并快乐的搭建历程，以后会好好经营哒！💯💯💯</p><h1 id="一、环境配置😆"><a href="#一、环境配置😆" class="headerlink" title="一、环境配置😆"></a>一、环境配置😆</h1><h3 id="1-GitHub"><a href="#1-GitHub" class="headerlink" title="1.GitHub"></a>1.GitHub</h3><p>（1）注册GitHub账号</p><p>（2）新建GitHub仓库</p><p> 仓库名为 用户名.github.io</p><h3 id="2-Git"><a href="#2-Git" class="headerlink" title="2.Git"></a>2.Git</h3><p>下载并安装  <a href="https://git-scm.com/download/win">git下载</a></p><h3 id="3-node-js"><a href="#3-node-js" class="headerlink" title="3.node.js"></a>3.node.js</h3><p>在<a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/">官网</a>下载安装就好</p><h3 id="4-检查"><a href="#4-检查" class="headerlink" title="4.检查"></a>4.检查</h3><p>检查以上各项是否配置成功</p><p>用<code>Windows键+R</code> 打开运行窗口，输入 <code>cmd</code>后回车，（就是打开命令行），分次输入一下命令</p><pre class="line-numbers language-c" data-language="c"><code class="language-c">git <span class="token operator">--</span>version  # git <span class="token operator">-</span>v不可以哦npm <span class="token operator">-</span>vnode <span class="token operator">-</span>v<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>出现版本号就是配置成功，我的查询结果如下：</p><p><img src="C:\Users\lenovo\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20211120153210085.png" alt="image-20211120153210085"></p><h3 id="5-hexo"><a href="#5-hexo" class="headerlink" title="5.hexo"></a>5.hexo</h3><p>确认配置好后，下载hexo，命令为：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-c" data-language="c"><code class="language-c">npm install hexo<span class="token operator">-</span>cli <span class="token operator">-</span>g<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>安装结束后可以<code>hexo -v</code>检查确认一下</p><h1 id="二、开始搭建😉"><a href="#二、开始搭建😉" class="headerlink" title="二、开始搭建😉"></a>二、开始搭建😉</h1><p><a href="http://beiyuu.com/github-pages">第一只参考~</a> </p><p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1mU4y1j72n?from=search&seid=12599429438714776447&spm_id_from=333.337.0.0">第二只参考~</a></p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_44507179/article/details/115306509?ops_request_misc=%257B%2522request%255Fid%2522%253A%2522163714954116780269890702%2522%252C%2522scm%2522%253A%252220140713.130102334..%2522%257D&request_id=163714954116780269890702&biz_id=0&utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~top_positive~default-1-115306509.first_rank_v2_pc_rank_v29&utm_term=github%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2&spm=1018.2226.3001.4187">第三只参考~</a></p><h1 id="三、补充补充🤨"><a href="#三、补充补充🤨" class="headerlink" title="三、补充补充🤨"></a>三、补充补充🤨</h1><h3 id="1-hexo的一些常用命令"><a href="#1-hexo的一些常用命令" class="headerlink" title="1.hexo的一些常用命令"></a>1.hexo的一些常用命令</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo new &quot;postName&quot; # 新建文章hexo new page &quot;pageName&quot; # 新建页面hexo generate # 生成静态页面hexo server #开启预览访问端口（默认端口4000，&#39;ctrl + c&#39;关闭）hexo deploy #部署到GitHubhexo help  # 查看帮助hexo version  #查看Hexo的版本<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>不过一般都用缩写</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">hexo n ： hexo newhexo g ： hexo generatehexo s ： hexo serverhexo d ： hexo deploy<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="2-文件夹的介绍"><a href="#2-文件夹的介绍" class="headerlink" title="2.文件夹的介绍"></a>2.文件夹的介绍</h3><img src="C:\Users\lenovo\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20211120163723479.png" alt="image-20211120163723479"  /><p><code>hexo init blog</code>初始化后，看到这一堆文件夹有点懵，去学习学习…</p><pre class="line-numbers language-c" data-language="c"><code class="language-c"><span class="token punctuation">.</span>deploy_git #需要部署的文件node_modules #Hexo插件public #生成的静态网页文件scaffolds #模板source #博客正文和其他源文件    _drafts #草稿    _posts #文章themes #主题_config<span class="token punctuation">.</span>yml #全局配置文件package<span class="token punctuation">.</span>json<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="3-git的常用命令"><a href="#3-git的常用命令" class="headerlink" title="3.git的常用命令"></a>3.git的常用命令</h3><p>很全！<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/halaoda/article/details/78661334?ops_request_misc=%257B%2522request%255Fid%2522%253A%2522163739863216780261927551%2522%252C%2522scm%2522%253A%252220140713.130102334..%2522%257D&request_id=163739863216780261927551&biz_id=0&utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~top_positive~default-1-78661334.first_rank_v2_pc_rank_v29&utm_term=git%E7%9A%84%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4&spm=1018.2226.3001.4187">绝绝子！</a> 还有一张很糊的大图！</p><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdn.net/20180620113451746?watermark/2/text/aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2hhbGFvZGE=/font/5a6L5L2T/fontsize/400/fill/I0JBQkFCMA==/dissolve/70" alt="img"></p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/sunjinshengli/article/details/53200423?ops_request_misc=&request_id=&biz_id=102&utm_term=git%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B0%E6%89%8B%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4&utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~sobaiduweb~default-0-53200423.first_rank_v2_pc_rank_v29&spm=1018.2226.3001.4187">此处</a>是新人上手区~~</p><h1 id="四、一些问题的处理方法🥴"><a href="#四、一些问题的处理方法🥴" class="headerlink" title="四、一些问题的处理方法🥴"></a>四、一些问题的处理方法🥴</h1><h3 id="1-hexo-d-后出现-ERROR-Deployer-not-found-git"><a href="#1-hexo-d-后出现-ERROR-Deployer-not-found-git" class="headerlink" title="1.hexo d 后出现 ERROR Deployer not found: git"></a>1.hexo d 后出现 ERROR Deployer not found: git</h3><p>出现原因 1：因为没有安装 <code>hexo-deployer-git</code>的插件<br>解决方法：在<strong>博客目录</strong>下使用下面的命令安装插件就可以解决啦</p><pre class="line-numbers language-c" data-language="c"><code class="language-c">npm install hexo<span class="token operator">-</span>deployer<span class="token operator">-</span>git <span class="token operator">--</span>save<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>出现原因 2：没有在<code>_config.yml</code>中写入<code>git</code><br>解决方法：在<code>_config.yml</code>中按下面格式写入</p><pre class="line-numbers language-c" data-language="c"><code class="language-c">deploy<span class="token operator">:</span>  type<span class="token operator">:</span> git  repo<span class="token operator">:</span> git@github<span class="token punctuation">.</span>com<span class="token operator">:</span>你的用户名<span class="token operator">/</span>你的用户名<span class="token punctuation">.</span>github<span class="token punctuation">.</span>io<span class="token punctuation">.</span>git  # Github pages地址  branch<span class="token operator">:</span> master # 或者main，之前默认是master，最新默认是main，可以去GitHub中更改<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="2-fatal-unable-to-access-‘https-github-com-39"><a href="#2-fatal-unable-to-access-‘https-github-com-39" class="headerlink" title="2.fatal: unable to access ‘https://github.com/...&#39;"></a>2.fatal: unable to access ‘<a href="https://github.com/...&#39;">https://github.com/...&#39;</a></h3><p>出现原因：一般是因为<code>git</code>进行<code>push</code>或者<code>hexo d</code>的时候改变了<code>.deploy_git</code>文件的内容</p><p>解决方法：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-c" data-language="c"><code class="language-c">##进入站点根目录后删除git提交内容文件夹rm <span class="token operator">-</span>rf <span class="token punctuation">.</span>deploy_git<span class="token operator">/</span>##执行这个命令git config <span class="token operator">--</span>global core<span class="token punctuation">.</span>autocrlf false##最后hexo clean <span class="token operator">&amp;&amp;</span> hexo g <span class="token operator">&amp;&amp;</span> hexo d<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_33349365/article/details/101514412">这里还有个git clone时出现此情况的解决方法</a></p><h3 id="3-error-src-refspec-xxx-does-not-match-any-error-failed-to-push-some-refs-to"><a href="#3-error-src-refspec-xxx-does-not-match-any-error-failed-to-push-some-refs-to" class="headerlink" title="3. error: src refspec xxx does not match any / error: failed to push some refs to"></a>3. error: src refspec xxx does not match any / error: failed to push some refs to</h3><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/u014361280/article/details/109703556">解决方法！超详细~</a></p><h3 id="4-config-yml的配置修改"><a href="#4-config-yml的配置修改" class="headerlink" title="4._config.yml的配置修改"></a>4._config.yml的配置修改</h3><p>一定！配置中，“:”后面一定加空格；符号基本都为英文（除了自己内容里面的）；缩进格式要正确</p><h3 id="5-hexo-d错误：fatal-unable-to-auto-detect-email-address"><a href="#5-hexo-d错误：fatal-unable-to-auto-detect-email-address" class="headerlink" title="5.hexo d错误：fatal: unable to auto-detect email address"></a>5.hexo d错误：fatal: unable to auto-detect email address</h3><p>很神奇，之前配置过了，又没了…</p><p>解决方法：</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">git config --global user.email &quot;xxx@qq.com&quot;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>我重新配了一次，ok了，还有个更高级的<a href="https://blog.csdn.net/nineya_com/article/details/103301870?ops_request_misc=&request_id=&biz_id=102&utm_term=github%20%20hexo%20d%20%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5&utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~sobaiduweb~default-1-103301870.first_rank_v2_pc_rank_v29&spm=1018.2226.3001.4187">方法</a></p><h3 id="6-如何上传项目到GitHub"><a href="#6-如何上传项目到GitHub" class="headerlink" title="6.如何上传项目到GitHub"></a>6.如何上传项目到GitHub</h3><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_44279615/article/details/114867844?spm=1001.2014.3001.5501">一只Link</a></p><p>目前好像没有用过，防止后面有用…</p><!--鼓励自己：~~在使用过程中难免遇到很多奇奇怪怪的问题，不要怕，你要相信你遇到的问题总会有一部分人也经历过，多去搜索，多去问，总会找到答案的，大不了，再来一次呗！--><h1 id="👻总结"><a href="#👻总结" class="headerlink" title="👻总结"></a>👻总结</h1><p>”试炼的终点是花开万里“，但我觉得，不止在终点，沿途已经有花在开了。就像每一次的经历，回望时也并没那么难，所收获的早已大过了痛苦，所有的经历都是财富，所有的开始都是征程🌸</p><!--这个分享比较草率，后面在虚拟机上的搭建过程敬请期待~~-->]]></content>
      
      
